## Component Checklist

Before building, verify you have:

- [ ] Git installed and long paths enabled
- [ ] Rust and Cargo installed
- [ ] Visual Studio 2022 Community installed
- [ ] MSVC v143 x64/x86 build tools
- [ ] MSVC v143 x64/x86 Spectre-mitigated libs ⚠️ CRITICAL
- [ ] Windows SDK (10.0.20348.0 or newer)
- [ ] C++ CMake tools
- [ ] 25 GB free disk space
- [ ] Stable internet connection

